RACE.FOOTNOTES: PRINCESS SONYA Broke slow, in hand along the three path early, gained to take on the leaders three across into the lane, quickly put them away and drew off. ROAD TO ROYALTY Broke the best, set the pace along the rail, was collared at the top of the lane, watched PRINCESS SONYA take charge and then finished second best. JACKSON AVENUE Unhurried along the three path, angled out and made a mild bid. ROLL'OVA Stumbled at the start, two path into the turn, three path out of it and weakened. STAR SPEAKER Trailed along the three path, angled wide and tired. WARTAPPED Stumbled at the start, rushed, tracked along the two path, gained to challenge briefly and gave way.
